Title: As a user I can assign product rating data with a valid path and body request
As a user I can't assign product ratings with an invalid path
As a user I can't assign product ratings without path
As a user I can't set product rating data with a request for the number of ratings exceeding > 5
As a user I can create comment product data with a valid path and body request
As a user I can't create comment product with an invalid path
As a user I can't create comment product data if content field blank request
As a user I can create new product data with a valid path and body request
As a user I can't create new product without path
As a user I can't create new product data if name field blank request
As a user I can't create new product data if price field blank request
As a user I can delete product by ID data with a valid path
As a user I can't delete product by ID with an invalid path
As a user I can get all product with valid path
As a user I can't get all product without path
As a user I can get a single product data with a valid ID
As a user I cannot get product data with an invalid ID (by entering the ID numbers, letters & symbols at the same time)
As a user I can't get product data with an invalid ID (by entering an ID number that does not yet exist in the database)
As a user I can get product comments data with a valid path
As a user I can't get product comments without path
As a user I can get ratings product data with a valid path
As a user I can't get product ratings without path
